[/url][size=6]Installation:[/size]

1. Download my mod and place it at data/skse/plugins/chargen/preset (if you don't have the preset folder, create it)
2. Open Skyrim using SKSE
3. Load any working save file
4. Open the console
5. Type showracemenu
6. Select the Nord Race
7. Look for the slide option "preset slot"
8. Select the slot 9 and press F9, this should load my character face
9. Customize your character as you please
